HASH_LENGTH¶

HASH_LENGTH is the expected length of the hash.

current value = 32

ADDRESS_LENGTH¶

ADDRESS_LENGTH is the expected length of the address.

current value = 20

Returns hash value within HASH_LENGTH

Arguments:
